  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > <strong>Escape from your parents house while being an absolute menace of a child</strong> </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Plan and execute hilarious escape scenarios to sneak out of your parents’ house to crash a party (that you probably won’t be old enough to attend).</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2782820/extras/0ab5d9dac2deec255bc906ff99d65029.poster.avif?t=1732193407\" width=600 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2782820/extras/0ab5d9dac2deec255bc906ff99d65029.webm?t=1732193407\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2782820/extras/0ab5d9dac2deec255bc906ff99d65029.mp4?t=1732193407\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Outsmart, fool and trick your parents to make the ultimate escape</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >10 fun and creative escape scenarios to complete </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Terrorize your parents and be the most annoying kid ever</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>HIDE</strong> from your parents<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2782820/extras/4e7a7247916f346fdaec326a3354dac8.poster.avif?t=1732193407\" width=300 height=140 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2782820/extras/4e7a7247916f346fdaec326a3354dac8.webm?t=1732193407\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2782820/extras/4e7a7247916f346fdaec326a3354dac8.mp4?t=1732193407\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>SLAM DOORS</strong> in their faces<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2782820/extras/27d5b00431c20a7370392c59deb3e224.poster.avif?t=1732193407\" width=300 height=140 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2782820/extras/27d5b00431c20a7370392c59deb3e224.webm?t=1732193407\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2782820/extras/27d5b00431c20a7370392c59deb3e224.mp4?t=1732193407\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >And be the ultimate <strong>TROLL!</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2782820/extras/f741f55db91e5d3a7615d337c61c4a96.poster.avif?t=1732193407\" width=300 height=140 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2782820/extras/f741f55db91e5d3a7615d337c61c4a96.webm?t=1732193407\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2782820/extras/f741f55db91e5d3a7615d337c61c4a96.mp4?t=1732193407\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >All while dealing with an annoying little dog. <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2782820/extras/c2cb88104e17e0dcc53eaa9730e59dee.poster.avif?t=1732193407\" width=300 height=126 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2782820/extras/c2cb88104e17e0dcc53eaa9730e59dee.webm?t=1732193407\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2782